aprove.Framework.IntTRS.Nonterm.GeoNonTerm

Class UpdateMatrix

  • java.lang.Object
    • aprove.Framework.IntTRS.Nonterm.GeoNonTerm.UpdateMatrix

  • public class UpdateMatrix
extends java.lang.Object
    Represents a square int-matrix and a labeling to the rows and columns.
    The i-th row has the same label as the i-th column.

    The application of it are the speed and direction matrices in the Loop used within the Geometric Non Termination Analysis.
    Author:
    Timo Bergerbusch
